Class PermissionsServiceGrpc

java.lang.Object
com.authzed.api.v1.PermissionsServiceGrpc
public final class PermissionsServiceGrpc extends Object
 PermissionsService implements a set of RPCs that perform operations on
 relationships and permissions.
